subject: Daytona 500 (Auto Race)
Nascar Sprint Cup Series
Automobile Racing
lead_paragraph: Danica Patrick won the pole for next week’s season-opening Daytona 500, becoming the first woman to secure the top spot for any Sprint Cup race.
